<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka kiengah um zingin Lalpa,
 Khawvel thima ka len lai hin;
 Nangmah ka phaw leh ka thaumei,
 Ka lungthim hun salh vak inla;
 Kumkhaw pielgal Na siem chu ei thilsak in.

[V2]
 Aw van Thagau hung lengin,
 Ka lunggilah hung chengin;
 Nangmah lo chu khawvel ahin.
 Muonna dang a um puoi;
 Lalpa hung lengin ka lunggil ah.

[V3]
 2. Hatloh leh lungngaih ni hin le,
 Ka hun ngai diek, Lalpa deihtak;
 Thachawl di'n chawlhna nuom Na hi,
 Ei puiin Na gam galmuong ah:
 Na thazak thiengtho chawnban lim nuoiah.

[V4]
 3. Aw Lalpa nei lungsietna hi,
 Khawvel ah tui bangin a let;
 A helo sang tamtak a um,
 Na tatsa taimangte a hiu;
 A pui khawm di'n Lalpa ka hun chiel hi.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Van Thagau</title>
<hymn_number>126</hymn_number>
</song>